m\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/88791&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15175659\/cocora-valley-colombia-guide-2.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15175659\/cocora-valley-colombia-guide-2-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15175659\/cocora-valley-colombia-guide-2-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Cocora Valley, Colombia: Hike along the World&#x2019;s Tallest Palm Trees\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-how-long-is-the-cocora-valley-hike\">How long is the Cocora Valley hike?&#xA0;<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The first option, the in-and-out trail, is a short 30-minute walk that starts in the grasslands below the hills. While you make your way between the fields full of cows and horses, you can spot the famous Cocora Valley palm trees in the distance. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>This option is great if you just wish to see the wax palms and don&#x2019;t want to do the whole trek through the valley. Expect to spend about 2 &#x2013; 2.5 hours at the palms, enjoying the views and capturing some photos.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25.jpg\" alt=\"cocora valley wax palm trees colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cocora valley wax palm trees colombia\" class=\"wp-image-81889 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10134853\/salento-colombia-25-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-conten