nt of the trail, the farm Finca La Monta&#xF1;a (2860 meters \/ 9,383 ft). Here you can take a break or grab some food before continuing on your journey. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11.jpg\" alt=\"hiking trail cocora valley\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"hiking trail cocora valley\" class=\"wp-image-90225 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colombia-11-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15172939\/cocora-valley-colomb