r the long journey. After 30 minutes of the hike, you&#x2019;ll walk past three viewpoints that look out over the stunning Andean Mountains.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10.jpg\" alt=\"cocora valley colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cocora valley colombia\" class=\"wp-image-90210 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154637\/cocora-valley-colombia-10-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1515463