\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9.jpg\" alt=\"hiking trail cocora valley colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"hiking trail cocora valley colombia\" class=\"wp-image-90208 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154623\/cocora-valley-colombia-9.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-the-cocora-valley-palm-trees\">The Cocora Valley Palm Trees<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Cocora Valley is part of the Los Nevados National Natural Park, which was formed in 1985. Before it became a wildlife sanctuary, there were many worries about the exploitation of these 60-meter tall wax palms. Lots of the forest was cut back, causing the yellow-eared parrot, an endemic bird of Colombia, to be on the brink of extinction. Luckily, since the conservation, the national park has been a safe haven for these stunning trees, birds, and countless other local flora and fauna.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8.jpg\" alt=\"colombia cocora valley hike\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia cocora valley hike\" class=\"wp-image-90206 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15154609\/cocora-valley-colombia-8.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Fun fact:<\/strong> the wax palm is Colombia&#x2019;s national tree. Most of the trees you see in the Cocora Valley are considered &#x2018;young trees&#x2019;, all between 70 and 100 years old. The wax palm tree species can live for over 200 years!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/tayrona-national-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The best things to do in Tayrona National Park<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-entrance-fees-opening-times\">Entrance Fees &amp; Opening Times<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The entire Cocora Valley and national park are actually private properties that charge a small entrance fee. For the in-and-out walk and the longer trail, you&#x2019;ll be asked to pay 6000 COP (1,40 USD) for entrance to the palm forest. If you want to do the entire Cocora Valley hike, you&#x2019;ll have to pay an additional 5000 COP (1,15 USD).&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27.jpg\" alt=\"cocora valley colombia birds\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cocora valley colombia birds\" class=\"wp-image-81907 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-150x194.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10141457\/salento-colombia-27.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>If you choose to add the Acaime Hummingbird Sanctuary to your hike, this also has a 5000 COP entrance fee. The park opens early in the morning, around 6 AM, and closes when the sun starts to set around 6 PM.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, choose to do a Cocora Valley tour that includes return transport, your entrance fee, and a guide for the hike.<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"59388P56,299163P1,59388P118\" data-vi-campaign=\"cocora-valley-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-tips-for-hiking-the-cocora-valley\">Tips for Hiking the Cocora Valley&#xA0;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Apart from the bigger cities, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Colombia<\/a> is pretty much a cash-only country. Bring some cash with you for the entrance fees to the Cocora Valley and for a nice lunch or coffee on top of the mountain.&#xA0;<\/li><li>If you&#x2019;re planning on hiking the whole loop, pack plenty of water and food for your journey. You can expect the hike to take about 5 to 7 hours. Staying hydrated while doing the trek and having some snacks on the way is important. After the entrance, there are only a few little stands during the hike where you can buy some drinks or a snack.<\/li><li>With all the rain and river water, you can expect mosquitos, especially in the warmer months. Bring some non-toxic bug spray to protect yourself from bites, which is also a great way of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/sustainable-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">traveling more sustainably<\/a>!&#xA0;<\/li><li>You can go to the toilet when you reach Finca La Monta&#xF1;a, at the top of the mountain.&#xA0;<\/li><li>Even in a cloud forest, the sun can shine on nicer days. Therefore, it&#x2019;s recommended to bring sun protection with you, like a hat and sunscreen.&#xA0;<\/li><li>Prepare to get muddy! You can expect your shoes to soak up some of the wet earth in this rainy region. This is part of the adventure but be ready for it with some suitable shoes.&#xA0;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15173142\/cocora-valley-colombia-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-90229 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15173142\/cocora-valley-colombia-1.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15173142\/cocora-valley-colombia-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15173142\/cocora-valley-colombia-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15173142\/cocora-valley-colombia-1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15173142\/cocora-valley-colombia-1-20x30.jpg