k.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/15173155\/cocora-valley-colombia-12.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"outfit\">What to Wear<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The weather can change very fast in the mountains of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Colombia<\/a>, going from the bright sun to lots of clouds and rain. In the Cocora Valley, the sunshine creates a beautiful tropical experience, but a completely different magical setting appears when the rain sets in. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Try to wear layers so you can adjust to the weather and temperature of the region. Throughout the day, the temperatures can range from 10 to 25 degrees Celcius. A raincoat and good closed-toe shoes are highly recommended when doing the Cocora Valley hike!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23.jpg\" alt=\"cocora valley colombia hiking guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cocora valley colombia hiking guide\" class=\"wp-image-88414 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/