/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">How to Visit the Cocora Valley<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Most people visiting the Cocora Valley stay in the neighboring town <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/salento-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Salento<\/a>. You can travel to this small colorful town from major cities like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/medellin-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Medellin<\/a> or Bogota by bus or plane. If you choose to travel by land, be prepared for a long journey through the mountains (around 7-8 hours). <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131302\/SA72364.jpg\" alt=\"salento colombia colorful houses\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"salento colombia colorful houses\" class=\"wp-image-81785 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131302\/SA72364.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131302\/SA72364-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131302\/SA72364-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131302\/SA72364-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131302\/SA72364-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131302\/SA72364-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/09131302\/SA72364-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.salt