=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It&#x2019;s, therefore, easier to fly from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/things-to-do-bogota\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Bogota<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/medellin-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Medellin<\/a> to Pereira or Armenia airport (around a 1-hour flight). From here, you can jump on a bus or in a taxi that will take you through the winding valleys of the Quindio coffee region towards Salento.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--flight \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--flight\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/salento-flights\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Find your flight to Cocora Valley<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100758\/salento-colombia-3.jpg\" alt=\"cocora valley salento village\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cocora valley salento village\" class=\"wp-image-81844 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1532px) 100vw, 1532px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100758\/salento-colombia-3.jpg 1532w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100758\/salento-colombia-3-479x600.jpg 479w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10100758\/salento-colombia-3-646x810.jpg 646w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\